Last July, Malcolm Harris had the opportunity of training and showing his game and skills in @gd_fabril do Barreiro 🇵🇹 After this experience, he returned to the USA to represent the @fcbaltimorechristos 🇺🇸 During his time there, he even faced @slbenfica during their pre-season preparation! 
Thank you for the trust and we wish you all the best Malcolm! 💪

#ThrowbackThursday #tbt #FabrilDoBarreiro #USA #FootballTrial

We are very excited to announce that we will be organizing a Scouting Event in Petaluma , CA 🇺🇸 between March 17th and 19th, in partnership with our dear friend @nuno.desimas from @rohnert.park.fc 
Tomorrow we will be announcing the first confirmed scout that will be attending the event 😎

Registrations will also be starting soon... Get ready! 💪

#ScoutingEvent #Soccer #Petaluma #RohnertParkFC #EuropeanFootball

@ac_marin_ 🇺🇸 is a football academy in California that dedicates itself to helping young players to develop their skills and their football knowledge.

Tomorrow we have a big announcement for you!

Don't miss it! 💪

#acmarin #scoutingevents #footballtrials #california #soccer

Dennis Misic is an Australian 🇦🇺 player that had the possibility to come to Portugal 🇵🇹 in 2019 to have trials. Through SunVoyage Sports, it was possible to have him play in @Futebol Clube de Famalicão - Futebol SAD  U19 team!

We hope this was an unforgettable experience for you! 💪 
#ThrowbackThursday #tbt #FootballTrials

Back in 2018 and already with experience as a goalkeeper in Canadian 🇨🇦 and Indian 🇮🇳 football, Sunny Dhaliwal had the opportunity to come to @osbelenenses 🇵🇹 through us!

All the best Sunny and keep hustling 💪
#FootballTrial #India #Belenenses

It is time to remember one of our partners, Rohnert Park FC 🇺🇸, in the person of Mr. Nuno Simas!

Together we are planning some very interesting developments that we will announce soon! 🙏

Stay tuned! 💪

#rohnertparkfc #scoutingevents #footballtrials #california #soccer

Partnership Announcement 🤝

It is an enormous pleasure to announce that we partnered with a great person and a great footballer of his time 🇵🇹 With a career in clubs like @slbenfica , @sportingclubedebraga , @estorilpraiasad , among others, he conquered: 
3 Portuguese Championships 🏆
2 Portuguese Cups 🏆
1 Portuguese Supercup 🏆

Thank you, @albertoblopes and we hope we will achieve great things together!

It is a real pleasure to announce that @kim__daeeun  from South Korea 🇰🇷 has joined 
@sertanensefc 🇵🇹 for a one-month trial! 
We wish him all the best in this adventure! 💪

If you also want to have a trial in a European team, just let us know, we do the rest... #FootballTrial #SouthKorea #SertanenseFC

정말 기쁜 소식이 있는데 한국에서 온 김대은이 @Sertanense Futebol Clube  에 한달 동안의 훈련에 참가하기로 한 소식을 알려드려요. 
대은선수가 이번 훈련에서 좋은 성가가 있기를 간절히 바랍니다. 💪

만약 이 유럽팀에서의 훈련을 원하시는 사람이 있다면, 저희들에게 연락주세요.
